  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK839">
<l>peritiṉitu pētaiyār kēṇmai piriviṉkaṭ </l>
<l>pīḻai taruvatoṉ ṟil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The friendship between fools is exceedingly delightful (to each other): for at parting there will be nothing to cause them pain.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
